These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, pop, reggae
1. the fan of reggae is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | country | pop | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, ferret, cat
1. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | turtle | cat | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | jet-ski | quad-bike | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | camping | filmmaking | hiking |

 #################################

 
