.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, romance, action
1. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | romance | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, cola
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda | cola |

