.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is baking##2
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | photography | filmmaking | baking |

